data.name: txtBoxInstructClassSignUp.Text
data.value: 1. Goto Person ID Look Up, Find Person's ID 2. Enter Person ID number in Person ID box 3. Click Cursor into First Name box - (First and Last Names Auto Fill) 4. Select payment type 5. If Check, enter Check number. If not skip 6. Enter Voucher amount in box if applies 7. Goto Scheduled Classes, Check all boxes of Classes paid for 8. Click on Save Transaction button

data.name: txtBoxInstructNewMem.Text
data.value: 1. Enter First and Last Names into Field 2. (Person ID should auto fill) 3. Select Payment type 4. Select Membership Type (I,F) 5. If Family, enter Other Person nfo 6. Click on Save Transaction button
